headline.main: Manchester United Held as Zlatan Misfires, Leicester Win Again
headline.print_headline: Manchester United Held as Zlatan Misfires, Leicester Win Again

lead_paragraph: Manchester United wasted the chance to move into the top five of the Premier League as their League Cup-winning hero Zlatan Ibrahimovic missed a penalty and 10-man Bournemouth battled to snatch an eventful 1-1 draw at Old Trafford on Saturday.
